<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1197381-does-anyone-know-how-much-of-the">Does anyone know how much of the novelization was written by Silverberg, how much by Asimov? Their styles are compatible if not precisely similar. The third section (the weakest, IMO) definitely reads like Silverberg; it has a lot of his typical internal dialog with characteristic repititions: &quot;Yes. Yes.&quot; etc.</a>
